<p dir="ltr"> </p>
<p dir="ltr"><u><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;"><strong>District Communications</strong></span></span></u></p>
<p dir="ltr"><a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1AwiduqezjU371P9q2jUiUzq-IH3wg-bS/view?usp=sharing"><span style="color:#800000;"><u><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;">April 6th, 2020: District Update from Mr. Schmidt</span></span></u></span></a></p>
