<p dir="ltr"><u><a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1Yusfep5ce8mGnM7pLSTxTGv6qoYVzSkLqHwZh2NGPs8/edit?usp=sharing"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;">March 18, 2020: Community Update</span></span></a></u></p>
<p dir="ltr"><u><a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/12CeReCE2slSXgIWtM55AQqB10w6MIeocxiwITDF9dzo/edit?usp=sharing"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;">March 16, 2020:</span></span></a><a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/12CeReCE2slSXgIWtM55AQqB10w6MIeocxiwITDF9dzo/edit?usp=sharing"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;">Update for Families </span></span></a></u></p>
