<p><u><a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1dmFbgrFVI5xMMprj6TCnzWjAHj5kaV-k/view?usp=sharing"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;">March 12, 2020: Orlando Music Trip</span></span></a></u></p>
